-- Wachovia soars on news of Wells Fargo merger
-- 
-- Fri Oct 3, 2008 7:51am EDT
-- http://www.reuters.com/article/2008/10/03/us-markets-stocks-wachovia-idUSTRE4923C720081003

 

 NEW YORK  (Reuters) - Shares of Wachovia Corp WB.N jumped 64 percent to $6.42 before the bell on Friday after news that the bank had agreed to merge with Wells Fargo & Co ( WFC.N ). 

 The stock closed at $3.91 on Thursday. (Editing by Kenneth Barry)